Maintainer: Adrien Ehrhardt <adrien.ehrhardt@inria.fr>
Description: An SEM algorithm associated with a Gibbs sampler which purpose is feature engineering for logistic regression.
     Continuous features are discretized and categorical features' values are grouped to produce a better logistic regression model.
